782
01:08:04,257 --> 01:08:06,302
Aku senang kau menyelesaikan ini.

783
01:08:07,166 --> 01:08:08,411
Jika kau tiba di sana sedikit lambat,

784
01:08:08,767 --> 01:08:11,212
