785
01:08:12,107 --> 01:08:13,241
Orangtuanya...

786
01:08:14,536 --> 01:08:17,212
mungkin menginginkan itu.

787
01:08:19,807 --> 01:08:21,392
Jika aku pergi denganmu,

788
01:08:21,916 --> 01:08:25,392
