sesudah 2.000 tahun.

813
01:11:03,477 --> 01:11:05,576
Kau bukan tipeku.

814
01:11:05,576 --> 01:11:07,406
Bermimpipun jangan.

815
01:11:07,406 --> 01:11:09,792
